OL,3,CThief stole from church while priest
OL,4,Cperformed mass
OL,6,FA burglar who stole from a church
OL,7,Fwhile the priest was performing mass
OL,8,Fhas been jailed.
OL,10,FPaul Dwyer used a brick to smash a
OL,11,Fwindow as he burgled the presbytery of
OL,12,FSt Mary's RC Church in Clayton-le-
OL,13,FMoors.
OL,15,FThe 62-year-old rifled through the
OL,16,Frooms of the building on Devonshire
OL,17,FDrive before stealing a guitar and
OL,18,Fcase, and a passport.
