OL,3,CThief stole from church while priest
OL,4,Cperformed mass
OL,6,FLancashire Police launched an
OL,7,Finvestigation and Dwyer was recognised
OL,8,Fon CCTV footage by the priest as being
OL,9,Fsomeone he had known for many years
OL,10,Fthrough working on outreach programmes.
OL,12,FThe incident happened on the morning
OL,13,Fof July 6 this year and when Dwyer was
OL,14,Farrested two days later, the stolen
OL,15,Fguitar case was found at his home.
OL,17,FDwyer, of Devonshire Road, Clayton-le-
OL,18,FMoors, pleaded guilty to burglary of a
OL,19,Fdwelling house. He is a 'three strike'
OL,20,Fburglar, with three convictions since
OL,21,F1999.
